  "description": {
    "zh": "这个是给神枪手先生的，似乎他正准备到森林的某个地方去狩猎坏蛋们，要去一整个星期。这是我从他背包里那一大堆的MRE，打火石，电池和水得出的结论。到现在这些东西还留在我这儿。他需要一把M1A，装备Ultimak M8基座，Nightforce ATACR 7-35-56瞄准镜，T1反射式瞄具，HOLOsun LS321战术装置，以及20发容量的弹匣。人机工效大于20，总体后坐力低于400，总重量为7.3公斤或更低。",
    "en": "This one is for Sniper, it seems that he’s about to set out to the woods somewhere to hunt down villains for a week. Judging from the fact that he packed one hell of a backpack with an MRE, firesteel, batteries, and water. Left it at my place for now. He needs an M1A, fitted with an UltiMAK M8 Forward Optic mount, Nightforce ATACR 7-35x56 scope, Micro T-1 reflex sight, Holosun LS321 tactical device, and a 20-round mag. Ergonomics above 20, recoil sum below 400, and a total weight of 7.3 kg or less."
  },
